Package gui.components

Class Summary
GuiAnimationComponent  
GUIBin GUIBin is a graphical representation of the bin component that holds the parts delivered by the trucks.
GUIBreakout GUIBreakout is a graphical representation of the breakout component that breaks a partially cut piece of glass out of the excess piece
GuiComponent The GuiComponent class is the superclass for all components in the factory GUI.
GUIComponentOffline GUIComponentoffline is the superclass of GUI components off the conveyor
GUIComponentOnline GUIComponentOnline is the class for oven, washer, cutter, paint and UVlamp
GUIConveyor GUIConveyor is a graphical representation of the conveyer component that transfers glass around the factory
GUIConveyorArrow A graphical representation of a dynamic arrow on a GUIConveyor, indicating direction of movement
GUIGlass GUIPart is a graphical representation of the glass that is to be removed around on the conveyer
GUIManualBreakout Manual version of breakout to be used in non-normative scenarios Will be given a part by GUIBreakout, it moves it to itself, animates and tells agent it's done
GUIPartMover Class to represent the robot that moves the part around once its on the conveyor
GUIPopUp GUIPopUp is a graphical representation of the popup component that transfers glass off the conveyor
GUISensor Class for animation of sensor
GUIShuttle GUIConveyorConnector is a graphical representation of the conveyer connector component connecting conveyors
GUITruck The truck collects glass that has been taken off of the line collecting three glass parts and emptying itself on the fourth
